I an currently a four-year undergraduate student at School of Computer Science, Wuhan University. My major is Software Engineering.
After graduating, I will join the CSTAR of the Department of Computer Science at the Wuhan University as an incoming postgraduate in 2022 Fall advised by Prof. Jifeng Xuan.
My research interest is in software testing, analysis and related fields.
